WEBVTT

00:00:57.882 --> 00:01:00.846
ofet, ou pa tro souvan 
invite a bann dine.

00:01:00.870 --> 00:01:04.666
(Riye)

00:01:04.690 --> 00:01:07.118
Si ou travay dan ledikasion,
personn napa invit ou.

00:01:07.142 --> 00:01:10.233
(Riye)

00:01:10.257 --> 00:01:13.976
Ousua personn pa reinvit ou.
Mo trouv sa bien etranz.

00:01:14.000 --> 00:01:16.475
Si samem ou ka, ek ou 
dir sa kikenn, ou kone,

00:01:16.499 --> 00:01:18.276
zot dimande, "Ki ou fer dan lavi?",

00:01:18.300 --> 00:01:19.976
ek ou reponn ki ou dan ledikasion,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:22.076
ou trouv disan desann depi zot figir.

00:01:22.100 --> 00:01:24.380
Zot pense, "Ayo bondie, kifer mwa?"

00:01:24.404 --> 00:01:26.041
(Riye)

00:01:26.065 --> 00:01:27.688
"Sel zour mo sorti sa semenn la."

00:01:27.712 --> 00:01:30.322
(Riye)